data.description: Spacious Split-Level Townhouse/PUD with Abundant Amenities. Step into this delightful home featuring stunning vaulted ceilings. Cozy up to your fireplace in your stylish living room that opens up to a spacious balcony on the upper level. The unit includes a full bedroom and bathroom on the lower level, granting easy access to the patio for your convenience. Updated bathrooms, washer, dryer hookups upstairs, a walk-in closet in the Master bedroom, and a garage with additional storage space on the lower level are all part of the package. Community amenities such as a gym, pool, and playground are readily available for your enjoyment. Conveniently located just a short drive from Travis Air Force Base. This property offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to experience this charming home first hand!
